<i>noun</i>: 언어학 [어너학], 어학 [어ː학] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>언어학 [어너학]</dt><br>
<dd>linguistics</dd><br>
<dd>언어를 연구하는 학문.</dd><br>
<dd>An academic field that studies languages.</dd><br>
<dt>어학 [어ː학]</dt><br>
<dd>1. linguistics</dd><br>
<dd>언어를 연구하는 학문.</dd><br>
<dd>An academic field that studies languages.</dd><br>
<dd>2. studying foreign languages</dd><br>
<dd>외국어를 배우거나 말하고 쓰는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of learning a foreign language, or speaking or writing in a foreign language.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>